{"tid":1556252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"200萬香港人，有朝一日你地肯唔肯推倒「柏林圍牆」","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:25:33.000Z","uid":94312,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b11df731baf5adec58893b69f98218702b2bf7","tid":1556252,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOeehGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOeehGG.png&h=16fbe5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光，有一樣好令我感動既元素，義勇軍進行曲冇，<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CANTONESE</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1989年，柏林圍牆的倒塌為結束東德共產黨的統治，東德政府的倒台以及兩德統一鋪平了道路，一年後的1990年10月3日兩德最終統一，而柏林亦成為兩德統一後新首都 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錯不在人民，針對專制政權，推倒圍牆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廣東人都係支那狗，不了"},{"pid":"44188fd88299fc2653fa2fc0f615453d95f0654d","tid":1556252,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"廣東人ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深圳狗不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe7d73bf697b116ebb3cf6c5fe5f64527922842","tid":1556252,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"直線呃負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東關我地撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd2eafa5bd3ae78a44bccb02c36ee461800bbf2","tid":1556252,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"歡迎負評，只係想知道香港人點諗，我冇叫你去做，只不過中共係消滅語言同種族清洗係有一手，<br />\n<br />\n一樣有心水清巴打開po講過曾經令香港人自豪巴皇家警察下場將會變成兩面不是人的國軍降兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\